subject: College Athletics
Basketball
Suspensions, Dismissals and Resignations
lead_paragraph: Seton Hall dismissed Coach Bobby Gonzalez, ending his tumultuous four-year tenure a day after an ignominious loss in the N.I.T. and the arrest of a player.
